reviewText: I have to be honest and say that I bought this movie because I like Kellan Lutz.  He did not disappoint  It is an exciting movie with lots of winter sports action.  The photography was amazing!

I received the DVD in a timely manner and in excellent condition. I bought the movie because I saw and interview with Kellan Lutz, who said that this movie was already out on DVD and I never heard of it. I decided to get it and watch it. He was awesome in the movie. Definitely different from what I'm used to seeing from him.

Eric Lively is actually a great actor. And uh....
hot. hot. hot.

The movie's pretty.
It's a no-brainer but totally decent.

I two-dayed ordered this item and when I tracked it, amazon told me it had been delivered to my front door but it had not.  I was very angered because I needed it for a birthday. Amazon reshipped it and was late for the birthday I needed it for.
